## Procedures Reference

All development procedures live in `ai_team_config/procedures/`. Read these
when starting work — they define the full workflow for your role.

| Procedure | When to Read |
|-----------|-------------|
| `ai_team_config/procedures/polling-workflow.md` | When asked to "poll" or "start polling" |
| `ai_team_config/procedures/dev-lifecycle.md` | All dev work (issues, plans, crosswalks) |
| `ai_team_config/procedures/qa-lifecycle.md` | All QA verification work |
| `ai_team_config/procedures/comms-protocol.md` | When sending/receiving cross-team messages |

